high_descs: Turn and go to the dishwasher.  When facing the dishwasher turn to your left and face the counter.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the counter to the left of the sink.
With the knife slice half of the potato starting on the left  that is on the counter.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink to the right of the red apple.
Turn and go to the counter where the sliced potato is.
Pick up the second slice of potato from the left.
With the potato slice in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the potato slice in front of the apple and to the left of the knife.
Pick up the knife that is to the right of the red apple in the sink.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and slice the potato on the second shelf in front of the lettuce. Start slicing from the back to the center of the potato.
With the knife in hand go to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink to the right of the red apple.
Turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge. Pick up a piece of slice potato that is in the middle of the potato. Shut the fridge.
With the potato slice in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink behind the potato slice and in front of the red apple.
anns.task_desc: Slice two potatoes and place the slices in the sink.
